{"tid":2109407,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★消息：蘋果本月首周內地下架逾2500款手遊","createTime":"2020-07-15T08:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T11:37:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c57ce03c7fb712e34bd2acf9a06947a274d7cd8a","tid":2109407,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:27:04.000Z","msg":"應用(App)分析公司SensorTower的資料顯示，蘋果公司本月第一個星期從中國App Store下架2500多款手機遊戲，是6月同期的4倍。<br />\n<br />\n根據SensorTower，7月至今被下架的知名遊戲包括Supercell的卡通農場(Hay Day)、Flaregames的無敵查克諾里斯(Nonstop Chuck Norris)，以及Zynga的紙牌遊戲(Solitaire)。被下架的遊戲在內地總計錄得3470萬美元收入，累計下載量超過1.33億次。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果未有回覆外電查詢。<br />\n<br />\nSensorTower說，目前無法確定每款遊戲下架的原因，但下架量大幅增加值得關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537879-20200715.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537879-20200715.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5GuwEiaVT8aWta%2BTWQuzHxyy8%3D&h=1da89005\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537879-20200715.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=de6d03e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537879-20200715.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9ee087c0ab56cbafe46f60e502e2a8f98d6f3d0b","tid":2109407,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f717387943f0bc022660fd15147cdc275bc8fd9e","tid":2109407,"uid":211062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"